# === Hermes / user-context-leak guards ===
# The terminal tool's "subdirectory context discovery" can drop AGENTS.md,
# llms.txt, and .agents/ into the working tree of a freshly-cloned repo.
# These are the user's GLOBAL workflow files — they MUST NOT be committed
# to a public repo. The .gitignore below blocks them by name in addition
# to the upstream's defaults.
AGENTS.md
llms.txt
.agents/
